title: Envy's Whoremaster
description:
My version of Whoremaster. I spent hours re-configuring the girls and switched out some of the default images. This is vanilla Whoremaster with a patch to make all functions work. It also includes some item packs I found on the forum and every girl pack was edited and chosen by me personally. I welcome any and all feedback.

Keep in mind, Whoremaster is a free game anyone can download, play or edit.
